{"tid":394593,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"放唔低 唔想放低","createTime":"2017-09-10T05:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T15:14:22.000Z","uid":134133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d743c7a1cc9b35609dbaf857164f0a33416387a","tid":394593,"uid":134133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:57:21.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊左年半，差唔多每一日都係埋一齊<br />\n陪佢渡過左好多難關，但喺我最唔開心最需要佢支持既時候，佢離開咗我<br />\n咁耐以黎，大家都付出左好多，但就係付出得越多就越唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分開左半年，呢半年好難受<br />\n有試過搵多啲野做，去識下朋友<br />\n但完全無心機，好似得個軀殼無左靈魂咁<br />\n好清楚自己無咁容易可以放得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c4151aa0be4b8698e4ee2407a676a466d3462f","tid":394593,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611dec204ec9d5775071936a2b30dd1279d1ea5a","tid":394593,"uid":134133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2f2d35041c556f7b4d031a42a342eaca78ac8c","tid":394593,"uid":130342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:07:27.000Z","msg":"分左一年了 依然垃圾"},{"pid":"0cb667158c3c45b7328095c4d3dbab2e9d03a271","tid":394593,"uid":134133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左一年了 依然垃圾</blockquote><br />\n巴打仲會唔會掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b92a365bc64cf6ddfdca57a814c01232ca691b","tid":394593,"uid":130342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分左一年了 依然垃圾</blockquote><br />\n巴打仲會唔會掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日